      "description": "### Event Handler\n\nAfter defining your domain model and services you can implement event handlers reacting to events triggered by these services. This file, for example, showcases an [event handler](https://cap.cloud.sap/docs/java/provisioning-api) for the `CatalogService`. There are various handler implementations reacting to specific [event phases](https://cap.cloud.sap/docs/java/provisioning-api#phases), as showcased in the next steps of this tour.",
